{
  "title": "Golden Crisp Uruguayan Bamboo Shoot Stew",
  "description": "A resinous and crisp Uruguayan dish featuring bamboo shoot, this stew is a crowd-pleaser and can be made in a claypot, it is also shojin-friendly and emulsifies well",
